FeedPackage.Description: MapSurfer.NET provides an advanced set of features to render both vector and raster maps of highest quality. Requirements: Windows 7 or greater, Microsoft Visual C++ 2017 Redistributable, GDAL (optional).

Marathon UDP is an industrial communication protocol specificaly developped for Inertia Systemes Hyperion Programmable Automation System (P.A.S.).

This project aims to give .NET developers the tools necessary for the realization of applications compatible with Marathon UDP.
